pre_pr_migrator_status.python39: not solvable: ['win_64_numpy1.19python3.9.____cpython: Encountered problems while solving.\nProblem: nothing provides vc 10.* needed by python-3.4.5-0\n']

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}

package:
  name: george
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/g/george/george-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3c88304b4a816c41b01198c084e3107ba7b0ab43881c60d249829eb2321245b1
  patches:
    - 0001-fix-windows-data-types.patch

build:
  number: 5
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - numpy                                  # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - pybind11                               # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - numpy                                  # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}

  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - pybind11
    - numpy
    - setuptools_scm
    - toml

  run:
    - python
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - scipy
    - setuptools  # [win]
    - vs2015_runtime  # [win]

test:
  imports:
    - george

about:
  home: https://github.com/dfm/george
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Fast and flexible Gaussian Process regression in Python
  doc_url: http://george.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/dfm/george

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hellovenkat
    - scopatz
    - dfm
